info.description:
Code intelligence ported from Open Komodo Editor. Supports all the languages
Komodo Editor supports for Code Intelligence (CIX, CodeIntel2):

Go, JavaScript, Mason, XBL, XUL, RHTML, SCSS, Python, HTML, Ruby, Python3, XML,
Sass, XSLT, Django, HTML5, Perl, CSS, Twig, Less, Smarty, Node.js, Tcl,
TemplateToolkit, PHP.
info.keywords: codeintel intellisense autocomplete ide languages python go javascript mason xbl xul rhtml scss python html ruby python3 xml sass xslt django html5 perl css twig less smarty node tcl templatetoolkit php
info.name: CodeIntel
